### 发送验证码（用于修改密码）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/send-verification-code?phoneNumber=13800138000&businessType=UPDATE_PASSWORD
Content-Type: application/json

### 修改密码（通过查询参数）
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/users/{{userId}}/password?phoneNumber=13800138000&verificationCode={{verificationCode}}&newPassword=newPassword123

### 修改密码（通过请求体）
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/users/{{userId}}/password/body
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "13800138000",
  "verificationCode": "{{verificationCode}}",
  "newPassword": "newPassword123"
}

### 获取用户信息
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/{{userId}}